FBIS3-23453 "jptot013__l94134" JPRS-TOT-94-013-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 21 March 1994 WEST EUROPE ITALY Disgruntled Criminal Hijacks Plane at Rome Airport Hijacker Surrenders AU2103131494 Paris AFP in English 1311 GMT 21 Mar 94 AU2103131494 Paris AFP Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Rome, March 21 (AFP) -- A Sicilian hijacker who held 160 people hostage aboard a plane at Fiumicino Airport here Monday gave himself up, airport officials announced. Giuseppe Cizio was arrested when he left the DC-9 jetliner to negotiate with a judge and a policeman.
